title: Samurai Pizza Cats + Kyatto Ninden Teyandee complete dvd rip
description:
Samurai Pizza Cats & the original Unedited Japanese version known as Kyatto Ninden Teyandee. Pizza Cats and Kyatto Ninden were release as two separate dvd sets because when Saban brought Kyatto Ninden over to the US, they edited the footage and completely rewrote the dialogues, making the usual dual audio/subtitle dvd release pretty much impossible. I know 25gig is a lot to download and upload, but please help and seed both series when you're done.

Samurai Pizza Cats: English audio only
Kyatto Ninden Teyandee: Japanese audio, English subtitle
